v><span></span></div><div>This was the bonfire we were sitting by. I can still remember the cold air and the warm, crackly smell of the fire to this day, almost 5 years later.

Edit: I have another post on my account, that shares backstory on my story of this experience. This is a minor part of that story, but I felt like sharing anyways.

